title: rtmpdump-all-versions-Source-and-binaries-Linux_MacOSX_Windows_v
description:

at http://rtmpdump.sf.net/ before this was taken down following a DMCA takedown
see http://linuxcentre.net/rtmpdump-can-be-used-to-download-copyrighted-works-like-a-web-browser/ and http://www.chillingeffects.org/anticircumvention/notice.cgi?NoticeID=25159
